{"tid":803376,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【學英文學中史】Youtube 蒙古/元 vs 南宋 戰略史","createTime":"2018-09-02T08:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T09:28:37.000Z","uid":99268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"298210adc3d3c8c363f0787d5199037aba013b24","tid":803376,"uid":99268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2iU66wzMy3Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2iU66wzMy3Y&d=%2FGfR7hlU0oN0UP%2BRcjWjXVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=2f0b851e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2iU66wzMy3Y</a><br />\n<br />\n之前做過 中國 vs 匈奴 戰略史，今次做蒙古 vs 南宋 （1230s - 1274)既戰略：<br />\n<br />\n1) 南宋同蒙古開戰，唔單止因為收復故土，亦因為覺得自己有長江天險，唔需要妥協;<br />\n<br />\n2) 窩闊台唔全力攻宋，蒙哥入侵四川既戰略，都基於同一個考慮 - 避免同宋水軍硬碰；<br />\n<br />\n3) 賈似道戰略上其實有見識，但係襄樊之戰羅唔到話事權，導致最後失敗；<br />\n<br />\n4) 襄樊之戰失利對宋既最大損害唔係『失去天險』，而係失去老練既水軍，令忽必烈可以渡江；<br />\n<br />\n5) 末代宋朝皇帝除了流亡東南亞以外，亦可以考慮係廣西、雲南建立基地，用『越南模式』抗元（當然都係兇多吉少）。"},{"pid":"2102ffce228d8d153bc3615abe959fe9b584c350","tid":803376,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"點解要用英文學中史？"},{"pid":"c7cb49b4b48aa47aafb29975666dcb54fb9b7e15","tid":803376,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2102ffce228d8d153bc3615abe959fe9b584c350","tid":803376,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"點解要用英文學中史？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"熱狗又搞事"},{"pid":"f599d3a4bea6ef0cbd009aacddd8430d508c3f24","tid":803376,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7cb49b4b48aa47aafb29975666dcb54fb9b7e15","tid":803376,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2102ffce228d8d153bc3615abe959fe9b584c350","tid":803376,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"點解要用英文學中史？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-0